      <name>Steve Hanson</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note that it is possible and practical to create a DFDL schema to model BOMs explicitly, so dropping support does not mean that documents with BOMs become unparsable.&lt;/p&gt;    </content>
